<center>

<h3>Jail</h3>

Landing on Pyrite Town Jail by rolling dices does nothing.

<br><br>The only way to enter Pyrite Town Jail is by triggering the Hacking Lady Monita Action event.<br><br>

<table align="center" border="2" style="text-align: center" cellpadding="5">
<tr><td><b>Rounds in Jail</b></td><td><b>Jellicent</b></td><td><b>Klefki</b></td></tr>
<tr><td>First three rounds</td><td>Choose to escape by using 100 Poke or a Jellicent card, or roll dices.</td><td>Choose to escape by using 1 key or a Klefki card, or roll dices.</td></tr>
<tr><td>The fourth round</td><td>Forced to use 100 Poke or a Jellicent card to escape. Eliminated if you have neither.</td><td>Forced to use 1 key or a Klefki card to escape. Eliminated if you have neither.</td></tr>
</table>


